{"tid":2511724,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"推！有隻腎衰竭嘅貓貓急需捐血","createTime":"2021-05-01T06:27:25.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-01T07:23:57.000Z","uid":171173,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"01e32934f6e47de675cbdda28a8dd8b235bc0ef9","tid":2511724,"uid":171173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-01T06:27:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmYhxoza1rYqZXRTeMgHpRWV7Zd9kCXnH96PNm1HVqATvy?filename=9JHqmhX.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9JHqmhX.png&h=e6d3f88d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmZZsnn7uKUhkwP7PVJs6uAbNuPAaeozfLamvtUgZ3ZYJL?filename=YvBCcpE.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYvBCcpE.png&h=8393cdec&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/Qmem4PHtqcpQmL6oVjsm5uKAyUpn2Ln2FRpyXQ4UiAPXYW?filename=rVqb1h1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrVqb1h1.png&h=14f758b9&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/Qmcv68PKeUEMGSE7iHxUWY6HTo7U5qQQRv3xkcoH3mzQ2F?filename=Sqn2owo.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSqn2owo.png&h=18abf9bc&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmQZG1wfnEcJwipr1MWstH19J5B83ptFXo68cmM8EZsiqP?filename=fn9Howp.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ffn9Howp.png&h=555c3af9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n求救🆘<br />\n<br />\n希望得到大家的幫忙🙏🏻<br />\n大家好 我的貓貓名叫 #豆卜 😺 宜家4月岩岩2歲 因為不明原因有慢性腎衰竭 睇過好多醫生都表示好難知道點解同搵唔到白血球長高的原因，當時亦好怕是癌/自體免疫病🥺 在1月發現嘅時候已經係3期 我地一直都有在積極治療與貓貓負荷中搵平衡點，貓貓和家人都沒有放棄！<br />\n<br />\n但佢情況近排惡化得好快 ，這2-3星期體重也由3.6跌到3.3kg ！😭而原本上星期Cre 亦是升到7.2 ，Bun 100之下，醫生和我們決定打皮下水的份量由100加到120ml，並打了造血針（當時(HCT24)！而今個星期的Cre反升到10.2 而Bun只係降到10😢 但最大鑊係今次HCT血濃度大跌 由為持左個幾月嘅22-24% 跌到17% ，而入院吊鹽水郁係一個方法好有機會幫豆卜的指數降番低，但係因為佢HCT血濃度太低 ，吊鹽水會有風險 😩加上佢血指數都有可能喺短期內再跌 所以希望宜家尋找勇貓可以輸血幫幫豆卜拉高番血濃度先，或以備突然出現最壞情況😭🙏🏻🙏🏻🙏🏻<br />\n<br />\n豆卜係A型血 重3.43kg <br />\n需要大約6.3公斤以上，有50 PVC嘅貓貓 <br />\n<br />\n希望有能力為豆卜做後盾嘅貓貓主人可以聯絡我<br />\n驗血等費用亦會我方支付<br />\n其他細節可以聯絡到再談<br />\n🙏🏻🙏🏻 請聯絡61601892 莫先生🙏🏻<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"red\">幫手推啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"8f2ac2855d37a0d7dfbef9e0bf297af7c1da7b34","tid":2511724,"uid":171173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-01T06:27:54.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"79c354048a70b6e7c6168a0fb530a8a0e8af3287","tid":2511724,"uid":171173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-01T06:28:58.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ad79df82ce50fd778a5037f4566e39b51da43886","tid":2511724,"uid":171173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-01T06:29:09.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f352ce7376fa3ae7048614032c396d2d509ecd50","tid":2511724,"uid":171173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-01T06:29:40.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"dbf25a79ebc5078daf3f12f543ae1db665d2f189","tid":2511724,"uid":171173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-01T06:29:58.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"43f7358945d09d6f786cd7801620cab0727e7fa0","tid":2511724,"uid":171173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-01T06:30:14.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a5dc876a134911ed44adef9dc08ac0d25088345e","tid":2511724,"uid":171173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-01T06:30:25.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d96d5c3ce99ae80e62257ca9f67a9896b16486e7","tid":2511724,"uid":171173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-01T06:31:40.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1085ca01d39218e2d5964c000f7613a08df647fa","tid":2511724,"uid":171173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-01T06:31:56.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"cc7070c45f9732fb89b9fea0309df64c25ce96da","tid":2511724,"uid":171173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-01T06:32:08.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ce9893